OL,3,CThree appear in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurdering man hit by car
OL,6,FThree people accused of murdering a
OL,7,Fman who was hit by a car have appeared
OL,8,Fin court.
OL,10,FLiam Green, 45, died after being hit
OL,11,Fby the white VW Touareg on Rose Tree
OL,12,FAvenue, in Cudworth, Barnsley, on
OL,13,FFriday.
OL,15,FMark Wigley, 60, Sarah Louise Wigley,
OL,16,F38, and Neil Shaw, 53, all of Royston
OL,17,FRoad, Barnsley, have been charged with
OL,18,Fmurder.
